text: "Things Don't Seem" is 1981 song by Australian band Australian Crawl. It is the leading single from their second studio album Sirocco. It went to number 11 in Australia in May 1981. ==Track listing== # "Things Don't Seem" (Guy McDonough, Sean Higgins) - 3:55 #"Big Fish" (James Reyne) - 2:42 ==References== Category:1981 songs Category:Australian Crawl songs Category:Pop rock songs
title: Things Don't Seem
